New York Governor Andrew Cuomo said Friday that 'Spice', also known as 'K2' or 'Mojo', is sweeping the city . 
  160 people have been hospitalized in nine days after using the drug . 
  120 of those people were admitted to Emergency Rooms in the same week . 
  The cannabinoid has been linked to deaths across the country . 
  Last year, California teenager Connor Eckhardt died after smoking one hit of synthetic marijuana . 
  Jeff and Joey Stallings were hospitalized in Mississippi after smoking the drug on April 6 . 
 